  m_Name: InstrumentSO_Banloda_Llanera
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  instrumentName: Bandola Llanera
  description: "Bandola Llanera l\xE0 m\u1ED9t nh\u1EA1c c\u1EE5 d\xE2y truy\u1EC1n
    th\u1ED1ng c\u1EE7a v\xF9ng \u0111\u1ED3ng b\u1EB1ng Venezuela v\xE0 Colombia.
    \u0110\xE0n c\xF3 th\xE2n h\xECnh qu\u1EA3 l\xEA, th\u01B0\u1EDDng c\xF3 4 d\xE2y,
    v\xE0 \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c ch\u01A1i b\u1EB1ng mi\u1EBFng g\u1EA3y. Bandola Llanera
    th\u01B0\u1EDDng xu\u1EA5t hi\u1EC7n trong \xE2m nh\u1EA1c d\xE2n gian joropo,
    v\u1EDBi \xE2m thanh \u0111\u1EB7c tr\u01B0ng v\xE0 k\u1EF9 thu\u1EADt ch\u01A1i
    nhanh, linh ho\u1EA1t. \u0110\xE2y l\xE0 bi\u1EC3u t\u01B0\u1EE3ng \xE2m nh\u1EA1c
    c\u1EE7a v\u0103n h\xF3a Llanero (ng\u01B0\u1EDDi d\xE2n v\xF9ng \u0111\u1ED3ng
    b\u1EB1ng)."
